## üöÄ **3. SETUP INSTRUCTIONS**

### Prerequisites
- Rust (`rustup install stable`)
- Node.js 18+
- Docker + Docker Compose
- PostgreSQL/Redis (optional if using Docker)

### Steps
```bash
# 1. Clone & setup
git clone https://github.com/jeantrail/jeantrail-browser.git
cd jeantrail-browser
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your secrets

# 2. Start DBs
docker-compose up -d

# 3. Install frontend
npm install

# 4. Build & run Tauri app
cd src-tauri
cargo tauri dev
```

> ‚úÖ The app will launch with:
> - 4-tab interface
> - Jean floating button
> - Local file access
> - Theme toggle
> - Mock AI responses

